channeldata.description: The Apache Xalan C/C++ Project provides a library and a comand line program to transform XML documents using a stylesheet that conforms to XSLT 1.0 standards.  The source package contains all the code to create the library, a command line transform utility and the documentation.  The documentation packages provide pre-built html documents for web browser use.  Binary prebuilt packages are available for some platforms. We could use help providing packages for more platforms.  Xalan is a project of the Apache Software Foundation.
channeldata.summary: Command line program to transform XML documents using a stylesheet that conforms to XSLT 1.0 standards.
